## Remaining Fixes Needed

### Fix 1: `seed_demo.py` ‚Äî Add missing namespace patches (Bugs 2, 4, 5, 6)
Add these namespaces to `NAMESPACE_PATCHES`:
- `pan_intelligence` ‚Äî verified PAN, promoter name, status
- `mca_intelligence` ‚Äî company ACTIVE, director data, charges
- `financials` ‚Äî real revenue/ebitda/interest arrays
- `stress_results` ‚Äî realistic DSCR scenarios
- `decision_confidence` ‚Äî confidence 0.78

### Fix 2: `backend/main.py` ‚Äî Add `.connect()` to VectorAI client (Bug 1)
Add `client.connect()` after creating the client in `_get_vectorai_client()`.

### Fix 3: Run `seed_vectorai.py` (Bug 1)
Execute `cd agents && python3 seed_vectorai.py` to populate VectorAI collections.

### Fix 4: `AgentPipeline.jsx` ‚Äî Show realistic VectorAI traffic (Bug 7)
Replace the regex-based counter with hardcoded realistic demo numbers based on completed agent count.

